Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we share our spiritual experience and what has come about in the transformation of our own life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:01:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with others so what we do is we carry the message and we carry the message primarily
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,intuitively and in the non-verbal although we describe the events within the verbal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the person gets from your aura what that is and it's the energy that you bring to the person
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and not your conversation so the conversation is because you got to say something in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and you hope the message might grab them but you only share it because spirituality grows by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,attraction and not promotion which is another principle of the 12-step recovery groups you never
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,see 12-step groups proselytizing nobody tries to get you to give up smoking drinking sex or whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they tell you i
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,used to be an abusive person and i had a terrible temper and i hit my wife a couple times and i
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:02:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,landed in court and and i really was scared and i couldn't stop it i couldn't stop it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and then i went to such and such a group and now everything is healed and i've learned how to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it and i learned a lot about myself in the process and i'm a different person and the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,person i've become now doesn't hit people so it's by transformation so spiritual steps then
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,are designed to bring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,about a transformation so we thought i thought i'd give a little time to the 12 steps because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,they have such a profound effect on our society beyond people's awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,people who are familiar with this very these various groups pick up a concept just like that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and i hear people in extremely high places in the world just with a simple remark i know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,how he cuts over and why he feels spiritually committed to what he's committed to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just one word will tell you what their background is spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so that pervades a great part of our current society see our society was at 190
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,human society was at 190 it's now at 207 well it didn't pull itself up by its bootstraps you can
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,see that by the pure nature of the ego in and of itself the ego isn't going to give up any turf
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,whatsoever so the spiritually committed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,people in our society are influencing others by virtue of that which they have become
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,not by proselytizing not by preaching but by by that which they have become in the presence of a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,more spiritually evolved person it is quite difficult to be vulgar and violent and selfish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you start to feel uncomfortable about it you felt okay with it on the street where it's the style
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but as you start to present the same story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:04:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to more spiritually evolved people you see them change at the girls ranch where i've been for 12
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,years i'm going to have to resign from there do like a time but we see hopeless i found another
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,doctor to come in so i've treated you know a thousand thousand teenagers highly resistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,savage backgrounds brutality brutality so extreme you say this is not possible this is not possible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and i won't even describe it here the experience is not possible and i won't even describe it here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiences are so grotesque so extreme you say that's not even possible i don't want to even
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,hear their history social workers starts to tell me this is their history i said i don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,hear it i just accept it's catastrophic and how can anybody recover from that how can anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,possibly recover from that it went on for years for instance and how can they well i'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't ptsd dude that said savagery you can't recover
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no psychological technique there's no medicine there's no physical healing you cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so how can you recover from it only by the miraculous the power of love
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so each month the girl comes in and you watch the transformation from ferociously angry ferociously
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,depressed assaultive suicidal they cut on themselves all the time they try to overdose
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,kill themselves and you watch gradually the flower blooming so you see that which is possible
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,only by love only love could bring it out of that savagery into become a beautiful young person
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so the damage then is spiritual and the recovery then is spiritual the people below 200 are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you can look at them as severely damaged spiritually whether it's by their own election
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's by karmic fate or by what up for whatever reason we now see that they are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually damaged people other than a powerful field this powerful field here is so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:07:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that it pulls the miraculous forth in those who have karmic permission to do so
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't always happen in this lifetime and you don't know with the reason for it you would have to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,see the karmic path away so you don't know what the reason for it you would have to see the karmic path
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the lifetimes, all the decisions, the context of it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the karmic pattern of the country, the ethnic group, the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You would have to know a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why all the steps that are profoundly powerful then
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,all require surrender of one's willingness and they all require humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why this one recovered and that one didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But the miraculous is commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They should never have been able to get up and walk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So we surrender, we start from the ego position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt, we share our shortcomings with other people, we look at ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and we constantly refer what's in the field to the field itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask God for help. We constantly turn our life over to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray to God for understanding. We pray to God for direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're constantly moving our tentacles out into the field
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and we say, in and of ourselves, we are unable to help ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only by the spiritual truth of those who have evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, everyone here, by merely being here to this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is already serving all of mankind. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the advance, just your own willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your willingness to advance your own consciousness already uplifts mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what can I do for the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing it. You're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of spiritual commitment uplifts by its own nature
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because it uplifts the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In previous lectures, we tried to align that for the skeptical
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with Henry Stapp's email or what do you call that website thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of Berkeley with the quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How he correlates quantum mechanics with how everything works.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So every spiritual decision uplifts the field of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the field then lifts each one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So each one of us then is contributing to the rise of the water, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the water rises, it lifts all the ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what their size, that are afloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So consciousness is like the sea. We uplift everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So every girl at the girl's ranch recovers, helps every other recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see great inspirational stories of people
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who have been savaged early in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of falling into and buying victimhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,they bought the spiritual way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see people of great prominence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the most famous people in the world had savage backgrounds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and they stand for the recovery through spiritual principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only through spirituality that recovery from that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and these things can come about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we've got a short time before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, let's try something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of just reading the questions out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody who wants to come up and talk to us, let's talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to be on, you know, everybody's going to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to share what goes on with everyone and come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll just come on up and gather around
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll just begin to really discuss things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got 15 minutes and then we'll take a break for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try it. We'll try it for 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody who's got a question, come up at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we want people to hear how it really goes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and not just in a lecture format.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just exactly how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd like to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sit down, right there. No, we'll just sit right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them sit there and I'll sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they need a chair too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Two quick questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, can you hear me all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They all want to hear your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Two quick questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scheduled for surgery next week and I'm wondering to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is having a local or a general anesthetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is there any spiritual risk associated with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any spiritual risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's a great answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Second thing is I've been suffering, I have constant fatigue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've had it for about the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going through the various programs and things you recommend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They still seem to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just wondering, is there something I'm holding in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's causing me to manifest this fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you tried psychopharmacology?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're knocked down all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is you can get like spiritually, psychologically depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the neurotransmitters in the brain change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, even though you've solved the original problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't come out of it because now it's taken on a life of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the brain chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's say you go through a tragic thing you've really recovered from,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but a couple of years later you're still depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because your serotonin level or some neurotransmitter got knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you just take it briefly, you come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you can taper it off and you don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything is physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all integrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't say, well, I just want to do only a spiritual way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because if you're really spiritual, you wouldn't resist recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did tell you that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, people do because of certain belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's intellectualizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if I was really spiritual, I wouldn't take Prozac.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're spiritual, you would take Prozac.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you serve God when you're depressed and in bed all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's of much use to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're up and around and being with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So do anything that might help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe just do something mild, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, very brief, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a lot of times the neurotransmitter goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, genetically, the human, don't forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,genetically, you know, about a third of the population,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,lack sufficient neurotransmitters to not be depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,About a third of the population becomes depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a genetic defect in the human gene pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're depressed for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's not like your mother got run over by a truck
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're depressed about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a reactive depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's endogenous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing happening out there to be depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why families give them a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, well, you've got nothing to be depressed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're president of the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's thinking about killing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very depressed, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you know, denial coming out of pridefulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're humble, we accept the limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of our own physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I can't jump six feet high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't jump six feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't climb that rope in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, grade school, or whatever it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm an ectomorph, and an ectomorph,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't climb that rope that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then away for one of those strength courses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, Charles something or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the world champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is back in the 30s.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I got lesson one, which was free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then for $6, you could get the whole course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, $6 in the 30s was, you know, like a thousand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was only one lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,how to strengthen your gastrocnemius muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I did that one over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the greatest gastrocnemius muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Later on, I ended up with an 18-mile trip
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to the paper route, the biggest in Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So those little gastrocnemius came around, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One free lesson, and I had the biggest paper route in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't know what the payoff is on these things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see how you've helped a lot of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because a lot of people out there have the same problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had denied that opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look, people believe it in all these spiritual programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even AA, they'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,well, you shouldn't take Prozac.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought I shouldn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's why I said to heck with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should I do, kill myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I kill myself or take Prozac?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, death is going to be on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that would be the advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is physical, mental, and spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,including alcoholism and many spiritual things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because the body, mind, and spirit are integrated, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know through the acupuncture system
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the flow of the chi energy and all that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're influencing our physiology all the time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the whole kinesiologic response is based on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So every negative thought or feeling is impairing the energy flow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,down some acupuncture meridian and impairing some body organ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't separate the physical and the mental or spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, they interact together almost as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for answering the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm sure a lot of people out there have had that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it does arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a lot of people in the AA, and that does arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my sponsors says I shouldn't take Prozac.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I have is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you say that death is a physical thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that death is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put this so that people can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should put it on .
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should put this on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That death is predetermined before we're born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I said at the moment of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or at the moment of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Moment of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,really there is no wrong way to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you can't really kill yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, wrong way to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the other thing we've found is that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,death is predetermined before we're born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the other thing we've learned so far
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the moment of death is already preset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How you do it is your own choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a big influence on the how of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but the time of it, we know, is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you tried to kill yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and it wasn't your time to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we've got permission to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't have permission to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just trying to figure out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...then really there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not our time to go, it doesn't seem like any way could make you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, that's bringing the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't the time to go, how could you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hypothetical impossibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So the problem is how you're phrasing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a real question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me the hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If a thing wasn't what it is, then how come it isn't something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I can't answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say it like a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you worrying about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a question because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just trying to stump the expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to figure it out because people do kill themselves, and then I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is only hypothetical to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer hypothetical questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only answer the real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about killing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody got any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody got any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How does...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, how does the I am teaching calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does the Don Hawk teaching calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're working on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to change this over to this side because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, there's 1000 spiritual teachers, techniques, practices, mantras, ashrams, ringing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of bells, gongs, incense, robes, shaving one's head, standing on one's head, 20 ways of breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Million things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we talk about non-duality is we want to avoid all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you follow the pathway of strict non-duality...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't get embroiled in that, because those are all dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-duality, you avoid getting sidetracked into the carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual carnival out there is endless,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the stuff that comes into my office is so mind-boggling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, nobody would publish this or follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The more bizarre and strange and non-verifiable,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the more skeptical you have to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the spiritually committed are notoriously naive and easily taken, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And some parts of this planet, it has become a great skill over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How to fleece the spiritually naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done with masterful techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so convincing that hundreds of thousands of people swear this must be a living saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The great avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's come to rescue mankind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, I get the name and some book by some great avatar that's come to save mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They calibrate 298.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can save mankind from 298, I don't know how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's romanticizing, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's glamorizing and romanticizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's the great avatar, you know, the great avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the next thing is they have many followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't forget 78% of the population,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't forget 78% of the population,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't forget 78% of the population,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the population is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anybody who's even at 205, if it's already an avatar, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To be decided to be honest in a world of crooks makes you almost a Christ, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my question is, do every human being come to this earth to grow our consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do every one of us share the same path?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's here for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That we were, if we'd reached absolute enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're here for the same reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,for absolute perfection, we'd be in some celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were hopeless, we'd be committed into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were hopeless, we'd be committed into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is more purgatorial because you see the whole range of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go from saint to sinner at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The freedom to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is to me like a self-healing opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, we had good karma to have earned to be in a realm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,where we have the option of undoing our past errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,our past errors and creating good karma for ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside of that is you also have the opportunity to create bad karma for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go up or down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So to me this is a realm of great freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At any instant you can choose to go up or go down and complete great karmic cycles,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,great karmic cycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So in this lifetime we see all kinds of transformations in all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the immense freedom, you see the immense range here, all the way from the most
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,pitiful bottom of the pit to the highest possible levels of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that is possible here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where else could you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:23:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,People want to come to America because here they see it on an economic level.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we represent the world as more than just economic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's greater than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So people are attracted to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What we mean by freedom is it's up to your choice to move yourself up or down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So this world offers the maximum opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,People want to wipe out something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wiping out that as a karmic opportunity because people were counting on that to get
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,them out of that last bad karma they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.54,0:23:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a law of war, now what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, you're really stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So some clarification.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The law of karma specifies that if what we do right now will affect the potential of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,choice we can make in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because of the simple definition, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very hard to get beyond the dualistic thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything merely is what it is because it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The sole reason for it being what it is is that it is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:24:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To try and jump that and create an explanation or a rationalization is moving out of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what it is because that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the self-identity is very hard for the mind to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It always thinks it is this because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.54,0:24:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it is what it is because that is the fulfillment of its potentiality as it is created at this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.88,0:24:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the position for free will then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.76,0:24:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just come to here to fulfill our potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.89,0:24:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because free will operates with limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the free will to be a millionaire by tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.89,0:24:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.89,0:24:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.89,0:24:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So we say we have free will, but the range in which we have free will or options is already
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.39,0:24:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,limited karmically, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.25,0:24:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now, what you are now has a certain range of options, and by other choices you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.95,0:25:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,may move yourself into another level where you have a different range of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.75,0:25:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A child who's half beaten to death and left to starve and sexually raped and etc. as happens
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.92,0:25:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to these young children has no example of love, no experience of love, and it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.64,0:25:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,have the option to become loving tomorrow, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.96,0:25:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have to put them in a whole field of love, and now they begin to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.79,0:25:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what that is, be considerate of others, they never thought of being considerate of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.92,0:25:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You grab what you want and what you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.75,0:25:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And hating others, they don't see anything wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.77,0:25:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They come from a world of hatred, so it's only now they begin to experience a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.51,0:25:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.09,0:25:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They begin to see different options, you know, to let a thing go and not hit the kid
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.06,0:25:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.06,0:25:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they never even thought of that, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.86,0:25:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel sorry for the kid instead of hitting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.78,0:25:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.34,0:25:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that option wasn't there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.45,0:25:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So somehow they have the sufficient karmic momentum to carry them into a therapeutic
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.21,0:26:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and healing environment where they can come out of it and survive, you know, spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.38,0:26:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.38,0:26:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you talk about spiritual vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.38,0:26:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.38,0:26:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You got one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.38,0:26:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I just wanted to tag something on what you were just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.38,0:26:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true and this person, like the girl at the girl's ranch, is in this certain
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.38,0:26:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,circumstance that she was born into, and in your book you say the average person only
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.38,0:26:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,can move maybe five points in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.38,0:26:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the average.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.38,0:26:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Statistical average, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.38,0:26:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but then I saw on the twelve steps you're talking about somebody moving from
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.97,0:26:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a very low scale to a 540 where healing can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.47,0:26:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm wondering, okay, how do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.47,0:26:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.47,0:26:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we know what's possible for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.47,0:26:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what I'm really hearing is all things are possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.28,0:26:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.28,0:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the miraculous is merely completely surrendering to God and then the possible
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.43,0:26:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.85,0:26:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is no actual limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.31,0:26:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it the person that moved or is it the event that moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.16,0:26:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.90,0:27:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know, when I said they move five percent, five points in a lifetime, that was just a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.69,0:27:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,statistical average for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.69,0:27:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How fast does mankind grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.69,0:27:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But the individual has no such limitation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.04,0:27:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often a person, you can go from the pits of hell all the way up to a state of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.69,0:27:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.69,0:27:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven and hell are a tenth of an inch apart as a fact, and experientially that's precisely
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.39,0:27:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.39,0:27:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,From the pits of hopeless hell, eternal agony, if there is a God, I ask him to help me, suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.56,0:27:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,into the revelation of this divinity itself as the only God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.57,0:27:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.74,0:27:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.74,0:27:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.74,0:27:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.74,0:27:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.74,0:27:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.74,0:27:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.34,0:27:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to say that the self as the allness of existence and the personal self went up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.34,0:27:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.92,0:27:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So one can travel hundreds and hundreds of points.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.92,0:27:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,People in these rooms, let's say if we do a before and after, you know, the average
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.85,0:27:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is maybe 10-15 points, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.09,0:28:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But within the audience, you can say and what was the maximum that any one person jumped,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.48,0:28:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you can probably get a couple hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.78,0:28:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So people go through huge leaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.43,0:28:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.26,0:28:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, for all the people who make a positive choice and advance in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.23,0:28:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there are a greater number who make a negative choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.86,0:28:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventy percent of the population is choosing to hate the SOB because it deserves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.89,0:28:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you measure somebody like Carl Jung and he's 5'40, he's 5'40 at that given
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.99,0:28:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,moment that he was measured or he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.99,0:28:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, if we ask now, see, don't forget, we're just sketching out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.69,0:28:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just like the telescope was just invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.91,0:28:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving a rudimentary idea of the cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.75,0:28:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything we're saying is very naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.86,0:28:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the things that we've discovered, you know, would in themselves just be a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.99,0:28:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,research project.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.99,0:28:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, you watch the evolution of consciousness and how it's spread across the map over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.06,0:29:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can take just minute little, small little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.54,0:29:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.54,0:29:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.54,0:29:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're trying to give a rough scale that you can roughly...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.63,0:29:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're trying to get is a general feeling for consciousness itself and how it grows
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.75,0:29:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.30,0:29:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And the awareness that certain spiritual environments are sustaining a spiritual growth and others
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.02,0:29:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,are deleterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.93,0:29:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And also what to watch for on the downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.93,0:29:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.24,0:29:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So does karma come from fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.24,0:29:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is fear the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.24,0:29:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.47,0:29:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma is a principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.47,0:29:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a principle of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.46,0:29:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that exists then reflects the quality of its existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is outside of time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.07,0:29:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when the entity leaves the body, that you take with you, that which you have become,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.76,0:29:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the result of spiritual intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.49,0:30:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual intention is what sets your karma and sets your calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.30,0:30:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.52,0:30:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the intention and not the outcome, so we become the consequence of our own spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.74,0:30:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.74,0:30:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.74,0:30:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual will sets up karma, not just getting mad because your fingernail broke or the filling
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.46,0:30:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,station was closed and it's too late or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.48,0:30:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those don't change your calibrated level of consciousness because your commitment, whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.55,0:30:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,your commitment is, is strong and it doesn't vary from second to second, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.96,0:30:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Major changes will change your calibrated level of consciousness, but it's not aligned
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.09,0:30:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,with the trivial from second to second.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.83,0:30:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the decisions you make to forgive instead of to hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.63,0:30:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All the twelve steps take you through the evolution of consciousness, to look at myself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.58,0:30:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the world, to make a decision to do something about it, to admit to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.65,0:31:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that I unaided and lack sufficient power to overcome this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.84,0:31:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you ask for God's help and understanding and then the miraculous occurs that people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.91,0:31:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly appear in your life who just seem to have the answers you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.43,0:31:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A five-oh-five dog just happens to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.93,0:31:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's five after.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.19,0:31:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I just thought we'd try this and if you like it as a teaching technique rather
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.71,0:31:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,than a didactic lecture, we'll do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.23,0:31:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can group, more of us group around and I can even go up and down the aisle as long
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.97,0:31:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as I've got this thing with me, you know, and we can ask if there's any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.76,0:31:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.76,0:31:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.76,0:31:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.76,0:31:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.76,0:31:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.10,0:31:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's biblical.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.10,0:31:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, it's real that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.60,0:31:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what we're going to do is we're going to try it as a different experience
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.84,0:31:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,collectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.84,0:32:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we're all together on this ship at this time and it affects one of us, affects
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.28,0:32:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.28,0:32:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm concerned with the happiness and spiritual growth and welfare of everybody here, everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.63,0:32:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,every single person without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.23,0:32:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.23,0:32:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll reconvene.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.23,0:32:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this thing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.52,0:32:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.06,0:32:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.50,0:32:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.50,0:32:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.75,0:32:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.72,0:32:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.72,0:32:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people don't know whether it's on or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.27,0:32:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.95,0:32:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.95,0:32:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.95,0:32:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.95,0:33:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.00,0:33:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.00,0:33:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a few questions arise during lunch, a few explanations.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.00,0:33:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to do more gathering together and having informal discussion and have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.78,0:33:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, on the sound system.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.24,0:33:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.61,0:33:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We all get to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.91,0:33:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some lectures, just the two people up in front are talking to each other and the whole audience
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.86,0:33:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,sits there wondering what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.86,0:33:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.03,0:33:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The audience, we calibrate, you know, the audience has gone up 10 points already.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.03,0:33:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,People ask what is the calibrated level of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.35,0:33:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulties some people have is in correlating the content of these lectures, which is called,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.38,0:33:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget, devotional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.38,0:33:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.38,0:34:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So they come to me with a dualistic question out of a dualistic pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.59,0:34:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning's, can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.04,0:34:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The lectures calibrate around 980.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.04,0:34:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.05,0:34:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.46,0:34:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The lecture calibrates around 975, 980, 985, 986, 986.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.46,0:34:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.46,0:34:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're describing a pathway which is extremely advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.46,0:34:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,985.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.50,0:34:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't always integrate that with a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.53,0:34:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.53,0:34:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a teaching that comes out in the 400s, 500s, or 600s.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.42,0:34:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's coming from a different paradigm of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.61,0:34:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the world that we perceive, does it have actual existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.61,0:34:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.61,0:34:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We already cleared that up this morning, that the world that we perceive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.09,0:34:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So it really brings up the problem of perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.90,0:34:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the positionalities of the ego, we have perceptions and then we presume that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.90,0:35:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,our perceptions are the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.46,0:35:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And duality means one transcends all positionalities and begins to see that everything is what
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.42,0:35:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.42,0:35:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dramatic jump in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.42,0:35:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can just see everything is perfectly what it is, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.17,0:35:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's putting the period on that is very hard for the mind to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.78,0:35:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind doesn't want to hear about periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.82,0:35:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.65,0:35:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants to go with why, delve into the hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.61,0:35:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Baba so-and-so says this, and the course of yuckety-yuck says this, and how is it group
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.80,0:35:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,says that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.80,0:35:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.80,0:35:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's their problem, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.63,0:36:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a certain teaching that the physical world itself is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.61,0:36:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next time you bark your shin, you ask yourself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.61,0:36:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that this dimension is unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.65,0:36:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that it's a different dimension, a different dimension that includes physicality and the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.15,0:36:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,experience of physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.53,0:36:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is really being meant by somebody like Ramana Maharshi, let's say, is easy to see
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.00,0:36:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,from this morning's lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.32,0:36:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you stop saying anything about the world, there's nothing to criticize, nothing to correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.53,0:36:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing that needs to be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.78,0:36:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.53,0:36:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This tree is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.09,0:36:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This tree is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.21,0:36:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This tree is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.25,0:36:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't mean this is a bad tree or this is a twisted tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.25,0:36:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What many people want to do is take these trees and straighten them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.63,0:37:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear the snapping of vertebrae as they do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.65,0:37:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Straighten you out so you see it their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.94,0:37:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.78,0:37:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see everything as it is, there's nothing you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.51,0:37:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you want to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.36,0:37:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't perceive anything as being needful of change.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.51,0:37:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You see each thing being what it is at the moment because each thing is fulfilling its
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.57,0:37:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic destiny and its existence is coming out of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.07,0:37:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to move through one's karma into the fulfillment of one's potentiality is the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.15,0:37:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,consequence of the enormous field of power which, like gravity, stands there, and in
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.17,0:37:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.88,0:37:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing goes where it goes by the nature of what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.88,0:37:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.88,0:38:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing goes where it goes as a consequence of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.90,0:38:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity is not forcing it to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.07,0:38:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To think so is an invention of mentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.07,0:38:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity is just standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.51,0:38:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.51,0:38:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The little iron filings with their charges and polarities are not really doing anything either.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.76,0:38:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.88,0:38:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just automatically shifting in the field as a consequence of that which they
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.88,0:38:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.23,0:38:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the calibrated levels of consciousness are merely how the little charged up iron
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.30,0:38:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,filings filter out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.30,0:38:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you go to the bottom of the sea, each thousand feet down you have a whole different
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.30,0:38:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.30,0:38:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of systems depend on the pressure of the water being four hundred times that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.38,0:38:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which it is on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.53,0:38:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's different consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.53,0:39:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, the sea is not causing it to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.63,0:39:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being that as a consequence of the reality in which it is surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.61,0:39:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I always forget what these lectures are about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.61,0:39:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody reminded me this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.36,0:39:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It says enlightenment, dedication, goals, and commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.32,0:39:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okie doke.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.80,0:39:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we sort of hit that this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.80,0:39:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedication, goals, and commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.80,0:39:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.51,0:39:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, what happens is the field, you're caught up in the field, and the field brings
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.15,0:40:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you to a greater and greater curiosity, commitment, a certain fraternity with like-minded individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.21,0:40:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal is to advance one's consciousness, eventually to reach God, which brings about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.25,0:40:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a dedication which expresses itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.25,0:40:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Which expresses itself as commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.34,0:40:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the commitment eventually becomes more and more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.86,0:40:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no linear way to describe it except that if we use the analogy of the sea, the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.30,0:40:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,water pressure becomes enormous depending on the depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.30,0:40:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As one gets closer and closer to the surface, transformational changes are the consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.30,0:40:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of the total field.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.30,0:40:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See, it's difficult for people to get out of a dualistic linear causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.61,0:40:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That my dedication is going to cause me to go here and reach that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.78,0:40:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.78,0:40:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Reach goal one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.78,0:40:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Got to forgive my mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.78,0:41:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.86,0:41:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.69,0:41:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's more a non-linear subtlety, but it is and can be and eventually becomes extremely
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.69,0:41:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.82,0:41:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.82,0:41:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire for enlightenment becomes overriding of everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.42,0:41:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's really the consequence of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.42,0:41:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As you keep surrendering the obstacles, the field gains greater and greater power.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.01,0:41:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And many people have walked away from what the world calls the ultimate, the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.23,0:41:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of success, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.23,0:41:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate in every department.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.23,0:41:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Status, money, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.23,0:41:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.65,0:41:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And completely walked away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.65,0:41:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And walked into some little chapel somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.67,0:41:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And got the, to me, the top job is the janitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.13,0:42:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The top job is to be the janitor in Shark Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.13,0:42:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the top job on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.42,0:42:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the congregation and the incense and all clears away, you have the entire cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.21,0:42:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which just knocks you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.92,0:42:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you don't do anything for hours at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.92,0:42:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you hire some kid to sweep the floor and dust everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.40,0:42:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you bliss out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.40,0:42:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can get just so close to the spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.55,0:42:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then as you get near level 600 or so, there's a tendency to bliss out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.55,0:42:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to watch with certain music as they start the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.55,0:42:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain phrase there where it takes you right through that phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.55,0:42:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just easy to just bliss out and begin to cry and forget the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.94,0:42:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.94,0:42:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, beauty does that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.94,0:43:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It wipes you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.94,0:43:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the presence of God is sensed as beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.94,0:43:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a few other questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.94,0:43:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I thought, we'll go on to, we'll do sort of like we did this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.94,0:43:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll try it out this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.94,0:43:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a confusion between intention and causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.92,0:43:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Causality is an operating principle made up by the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.92,0:43:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates around 460 to explain perceptual phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.92,0:43:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't explain phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.92,0:43:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It explains one's perception of the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.92,0:43:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The subtlety of moving from pseudo-objectivity to realizing that everything is subjective,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.01,0:43:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is very, very subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.01,0:43:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And people can study the subject for a lifetime and miss the whole point.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.01,0:44:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That the thought that causality explains things neatly within the Newtonian paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.71,0:44:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,still remains an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.90,0:44:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And within that which exists itself, there is no such operational principle as causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.13,0:44:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,which would be explicable in terms of physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.13,0:44:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower is what it is and becomes this potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.96,0:44:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,due to, operationally, an infinite number of factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.07,0:44:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we've calibrated in public before,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.07,0:44:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the number of factors necessary to completely explain
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.07,0:44:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,why one speck of dust is sitting here in the middle of the air
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.07,0:44:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is infinite, infinite, infinite number.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.40,0:44:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have the room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.40,0:44:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have the very magic pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.40,0:44:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.40,0:44:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have somebody that observed it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.84,0:44:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And for this building to be here, there has to be this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.84,0:44:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.84,0:45:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be this galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.84,0:45:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to go back to creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.84,0:45:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the explanation for this piece of dust here
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.84,0:45:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,takes us back to the question of creation itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.84,0:45:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Inexplicable in terms of ordinary consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.78,0:45:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When one first goes into a very advanced state,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.82,0:45:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the strange things,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.59,0:45:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,not in a very, yeah, it's a very advanced state,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.59,0:45:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,around 600 or something, high 500s or 600s,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.59,0:45:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere around there,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.59,0:45:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,during the course of miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.59,0:45:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a very not uncommon phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.69,0:45:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're walking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.69,0:45:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you notice that you're in love with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.69,0:45:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to notice how everybody looks handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.69,0:45:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody looks well-dressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.69,0:45:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody looks beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.69,0:45:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is gorgeous,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.50,0:45:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything is happening perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.19,0:45:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you also notice that everybody seems
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.19,0:46:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to be in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.67,0:46:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice that people are completely unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.67,0:46:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's two dialogues going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.67,0:46:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's what they think is being said and happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.67,0:46:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's what's really going on
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.67,0:46:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of which they are unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.05,0:46:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And they seem to be in a dream state.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.80,0:46:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the dream state they're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.80,0:46:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning we came up with
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.59,0:46:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what percent of the mind is silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.73,0:46:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,98?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.09,0:46:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.09,0:46:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're unaware of the 98 percent
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.69,0:46:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're so focused on the 2 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.69,0:46:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So focused on the 2 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.90,0:46:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what gives them the dream-like quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.09,0:46:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like oblivious to what's actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.09,0:46:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what actually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.11,0:46:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead they're like focused on the dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.11,0:46:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the 2 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.11,0:46:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you go through the course of miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.11,0:47:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as a common experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.11,0:47:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or through 10, 12 steps, either one,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.11,0:47:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can reach a state
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.11,0:47:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,where everybody seems to be walking around
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.11,0:47:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,completely unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.11,0:47:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in some kind of a dream state.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.11,0:47:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reality that surrounds them,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.11,0:47:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they seem to be oblivious, oblivious of.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.11,0:47:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.11,0:47:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone seems to be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.11,0:47:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Which tells you to walk around anonymously
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.11,0:47:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because they don't see who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.11,0:47:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.69,0:47:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is just loving them,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.69,0:47:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,which if they were aware of would scare them
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.69,0:47:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and they might call 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.69,0:47:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Love frightens people, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.63,0:47:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When you pull up to the next stop and go light,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.63,0:47:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,look over at the driver at the next car
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.63,0:47:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and smile and send him a love.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.92,0:47:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mildred, is that man smiling at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.92,0:47:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.92,0:47:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's either a lecher or a robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.05,0:48:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try it. It's just fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.07,0:48:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The next stop and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.07,0:48:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever's in the other car, you look over and...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.03,0:48:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute consternation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.03,0:48:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're gonna be a carjacker or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.42,0:48:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.42,0:48:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now there's other questions
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.51,0:48:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that we didn't get a chance to answer this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.51,0:48:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did everything we explained this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.63,0:48:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,seem rather clear and obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.63,0:48:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.76,0:48:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.21,0:48:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a great relief to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.21,0:48:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can experience your own death.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.21,0:48:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of death is set anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.21,0:48:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninety-eight percent of your mind that you're worried about,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.25,0:48:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego, already doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.25,0:48:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninety-eight percent of what you thought
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.63,0:48:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna have to do is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.63,0:48:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You only got two percent left.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.63,0:48:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What great karmic good fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.17,0:48:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,brings us all here to hear this lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.17,0:48:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I discovered it, I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.55,0:49:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, wow, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.78,0:49:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, everybody's 98% of the way already.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.78,0:49:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that certainly isn't heartening.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.78,0:49:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's only this lingering,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.78,0:49:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,like these little clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.78,0:49:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of the two percent
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.78,0:49:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have to unhook now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.78,0:49:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we see the mechanism,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.78,0:49:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, once you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.13,0:49:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.13,0:49:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it begins to dissolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.13,0:49:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins to dissolve
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.13,0:49:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as you become aware of its nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.44,0:49:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're merely holding in place
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.44,0:49:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.57,0:49:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you examine what is the reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.57,0:49:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing holding that perception
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.57,0:49:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.57,0:49:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And behind that perception
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.57,0:49:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is an intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.01,0:49:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There is the payoff to the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.01,0:49:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which we didn't recover this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.09,0:49:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because we recovered it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.09,0:49:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, if all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.17,0:49:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,are what is blocking us from enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.17,0:49:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and a state of peace and harmony and love,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.17,0:50:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,why would people persist in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.17,0:50:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all those positionalities
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.28,0:50:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that we looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.28,0:50:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,all have a payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.28,0:50:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have a payoff
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the form of juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.50,0:50:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And to be the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.17,0:50:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is so juicy,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.17,0:50:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really hard to give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.17,0:50:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To be right is so juicy,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.23,0:50:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.23,0:50:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge is so juicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.23,0:50:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, to turn the dagger
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.53,0:50:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the bastard's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.26,0:50:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's deserved it all these lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.26,0:50:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I finally got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.55,0:50:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.55,0:50:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the Middle East,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.55,0:50:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the glee with which they kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.55,0:50:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the faces on the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.55,0:50:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All the young men, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.55,0:50:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,throwing rocks at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.55,0:50:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in a state of emotional ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.55,0:50:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing each other for God,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.55,0:50:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for Jesus, for Allah,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.55,0:50:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever you want to kill them for.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.55,0:50:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever's popular in that culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.09,0:50:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just the payoff of that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.50,0:51:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is so enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.50,0:51:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To ask somebody to relinquish it,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.50,0:51:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to relinquish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.69,0:51:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you get this,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.73,0:51:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,now somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.73,0:51:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to hand over his gun
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.73,0:51:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and become nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.73,0:51:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,when by killing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.73,0:51:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,he's somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.73,0:51:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.73,0:51:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The payoff is so enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.73,0:51:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see that the core of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.92,0:51:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its stratifications
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.92,0:51:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that we described this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.92,0:51:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is a profound egocentrism.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.92,0:51:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The egoistic core of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.42,0:51:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is what underlies all the things
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.42,0:51:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we described about.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.55,0:51:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.55,0:51:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,because it does not live on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.55,0:51:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,has to get juiced somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.55,0:51:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and it gets its energy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.53,0:51:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by juicing negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.53,0:51:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.53,0:51:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some organisms
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.65,0:51:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that live only on dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.65,0:51:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.82,0:52:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego then,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.92,0:52:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is cut off from
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.92,0:52:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that which we might call
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.17,0:52:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the love of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.23,0:52:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,now, as though it lives in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.26,0:52:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,must learn how to suck juices
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.26,0:52:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that which is negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.51,0:52:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Its subsides,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.03,0:52:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,its subsistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.03,0:52:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,its source of ongoingness then,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.03,0:52:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is the juice it gets out of negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.03,0:52:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, if you ask the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.21,0:52:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of the juice,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.21,0:52:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you're asking it to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.21,0:52:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to get somebody to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.15,0:52:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,being the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.38,0:52:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.05,0:52:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.05,0:52:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch people on television
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.11,0:52:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.11,0:52:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They have made a career
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.11,0:52:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.36,0:53:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,juicing being the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.36,0:53:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're not the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.82,0:53:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you can make your child the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.82,0:53:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You get strange psychiatric disorders.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.82,0:53:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wunschhausen by proxy syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.82,0:53:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.46,0:53:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't be the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.46,0:53:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you become the quasi-victim
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.46,0:53:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,by having a child as a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.46,0:53:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the degree of pathology
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.61,0:53:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to which the ego will resort
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.61,0:53:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to ensure its own survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.57,0:53:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.57,0:53:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the power
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.57,0:53:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of the negativity of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.57,0:53:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the tenacity of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.57,0:53:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is the better word,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.57,0:53:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the tenacity with which the ego clings
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.57,0:53:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to being right, righteousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.57,0:53:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing others sinful, wrong, and guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.57,0:53:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,punishing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.57,0:53:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.96,0:53:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we want to put somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.59,0:53:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to death for anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.59,0:53:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,People get a glee that he deserves it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.59,0:53:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they punish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.59,0:53:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The only trouble with that is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.86,0:54:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you think people out there deserve
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.55,0:54:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is what your unconscious holds for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.55,0:54:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If they should die for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.61,0:54:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,unconsciously then,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.61,0:54:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your own fear of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.61,0:54:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so you cannot get away with projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.67,0:54:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ego survives by the paranoid mechanism
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.67,0:54:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of seeing evil and all these things out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.82,0:54:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What it thinks everybody out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.82,0:54:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the sentence that it puts on everybody out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.01,0:54:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is the sentence that you've put on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.01,0:54:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In psychoanalysis, the first rule is,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.80,0:54:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to soften up the superego,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.15,0:54:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.15,0:54:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,before you start bringing stuff up
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.15,0:54:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,from the unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.34,0:54:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because the superego is quite vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.34,0:54:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants to execute its enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.44,0:54:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and gloat over the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.57,0:55:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Extract every bit of pleasure it can out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.76,0:55:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.42,0:55:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the homicidal fantasies
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.44,0:55:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which are plunged down into your id,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.44,0:55:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which come out of the animal evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.44,0:55:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,an animal doesn't want to,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.44,0:55:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.44,0:55:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,prevail over the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.44,0:55:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he wants to kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.44,0:55:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the unconscious thinks in terms of killing enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.63,0:55:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.57,0:55:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the more we soften the conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.57,0:55:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then, towards others,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.57,0:55:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we're actually softening it towards ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.57,0:55:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The more we're willing to forgive others,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.57,0:55:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the more we're forgiving towards ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.57,0:55:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, they become one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.57,0:55:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And we become more and more benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.57,0:55:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we ask ourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.07,0:55:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,could I give up the pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.07,0:55:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in watching this guy fry in the electric chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.07,0:56:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people like to put it on TV and watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.78,0:56:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.78,0:56:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The macabre, the gruesome
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.78,0:56:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ego is really immense.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.17,0:56:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so the willingness to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.30,0:56:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the payoff of negativity
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.30,0:56:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is what releases it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.30,0:56:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When you don't get pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.84,0:56:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.84,0:56:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when you don't get pleasure out of being right,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.84,0:56:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see that everybody is doing the best they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.84,0:56:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So forgiveness comes out of the real,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.84,0:56:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the realistic understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.86,0:56:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that everything is only being what it can
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.86,0:56:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time that it's being that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.86,0:56:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the flower is only unfolded at this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.51,0:56:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,should we punish the flower or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.05,0:56:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it off at the stem?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.98,0:56:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should beat it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.98,0:56:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's a bad flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.98,0:56:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.98,0:56:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to see the ridiculousness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.98,0:56:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ego's positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.98,0:56:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As you do that, you weaken its structure,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.98,0:57:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you start pulling the sticks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.98,0:57:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego gets weaker and weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.32,0:57:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody in a group like this
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.32,0:57:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is farther ahead than what they think they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.32,0:57:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.32,0:57:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they focus on the areas
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.32,0:57:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're not pleased with.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.32,0:57:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're focused on what you're working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.32,0:57:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody has a view of themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.32,0:57:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as being worse than they actually are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.32,0:57:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't met anybody who's really awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.36,0:57:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.82,0:57:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are sort of warped individuals
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.32,0:57:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,who need help, I'll say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.59,0:57:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A little on the warped side.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.59,0:57:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, they can't help being warped.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.69,0:57:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of genes?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.69,0:57:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.69,0:57:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows why they are the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.69,0:57:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you end up with a full understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.69,0:57:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.69,0:57:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,we describe all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.69,0:57:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,non-duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.98,0:58:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is to transcend the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.98,0:58:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.98,0:58:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you understand the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.98,0:58:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the more it begins to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.98,0:58:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you find that compassion is a constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.55,0:58:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It already exists within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.55,0:58:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as devotion already exists within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.71,0:58:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is already within you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.88,0:58:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a well and a reservoir
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.88,0:58:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of intense and powerful devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.88,0:58:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that is far more powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.88,0:58:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,than what you realize yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.88,0:58:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when the great obstacle arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.17,0:58:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,much to your amazement,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.36,0:58:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there comes out of you an intensity,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.36,0:58:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,an absoluteness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.36,0:58:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that is willing to walk through anything
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.36,0:58:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach God.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.42,0:58:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It is like the gravity of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.61,0:58:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So the closer you get to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.61,0:58:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the more powerful becomes the gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.61,0:58:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the last door,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.15,0:58:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,where you have to surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.15,0:58:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,very life itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.15,0:59:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the gravity is so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.15,0:59:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a moment hesitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.38,0:59:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the words of wisdom that you recall
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.38,0:59:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from some lifetime come to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.38,0:59:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the trip is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.13,0:59:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you need
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.13,0:59:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is already waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.13,0:59:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to have it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.13,0:59:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like mountain climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.26,0:59:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you need up there
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.26,0:59:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is already sitting up there waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.26,0:59:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to look at yourself and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.26,0:59:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have within me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.26,0:59:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what it takes to make this whole trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.26,0:59:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.26,0:59:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't need it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.26,0:59:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get up to this elevation,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.26,0:59:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't need that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.26,0:59:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get up to this elevation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.26,0:59:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything that you need
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.26,0:59:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to go the whole way spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.51,0:59:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is already provided for.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.51,0:59:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fact. Fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.00,0:59:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to look within yourself and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.00,0:59:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have that much commitment,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.00,0:59:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have that much drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.00,1:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have that much certitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you get to the next block,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.21,1:00:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll suddenly have it,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.21,1:00:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and you turn the corner,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.21,1:00:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you go down the two blocks,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.21,1:00:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it gets more intense,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.21,1:00:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and so the gravity increases its power.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.32,1:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So nobody has to worry about their spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.86,1:00:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already certain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.86,1:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If spiritual evolution wasn't certain,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.13,1:00:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.13,1:00:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody would be here
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.13,1:00:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,unless they were scheduled karmically to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.13,1:00:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody else would be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.13,1:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The very fact that you're here
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.13,1:00:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is a statement of intention and dedication.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.13,1:00:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And a good 505 is back for a number of years.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.71,1:00:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be another trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.73,1:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to go around and answer the questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.80,1:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see how it answers questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.80,1:00:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.80,1:00:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the joy of its being what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.86,1:01:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,reveals to you the absolute truth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.86,1:01:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.96,1:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Its joy is coming out of its own existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.96,1:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it shares its joy of existence with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.96,1:01:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Interestingly,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.96,1:01:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,this one asks for nothing in return.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.96,1:01:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is like unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.96,1:01:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is love
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.96,1:01:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and asks for nothing,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.96,1:01:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't ask you for a pet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.96,1:01:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting dog
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.28,1:01:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that God sent for the purpose of the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.01,1:01:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So as I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.30,1:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what you need to explain the thing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.30,1:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is waiting for you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.30,1:01:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so that at the moment
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.30,1:01:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,when you need a dog to demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.30,1:01:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.30,1:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the dog appears.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.30,1:01:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.13,1:01:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If only for a dog,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.61,1:01:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,then why not even more so for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.61,1:01:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we realize that we are blessed
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.15,1:01:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,by our being with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.21,1:01:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing I wanted to mention,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.21,1:01:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we're going to go to questions
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.21,1:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and do it sort of so everyone can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.21,1:02:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd gotten a couple of letters of consternation
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.53,1:02:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.53,1:02:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's best to have somebody who knows you
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.53,1:02:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,realize that you're on
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.53,1:02:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a seriously committed spiritual path.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.53,1:02:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That person got sort of frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.53,1:02:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Family, friends,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.71,1:02:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody should realize that,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.71,1:02:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.71,1:02:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you're serious about spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.71,1:02:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And people who get serious about spirituality
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.71,1:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,are known to go into certain
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.71,1:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and rather advanced spiritual states
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.71,1:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which are not understood by everybody,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.71,1:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,including psychiatrists.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.88,1:02:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to have a spiritually,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.88,1:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,some spiritually aware friends
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.88,1:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who realize what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.88,1:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.88,1:02:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you sit there and begin to meditate,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.88,1:02:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you start surrendering everything as it arises,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.88,1:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,one can go in a state of bliss.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.88,1:02:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That is in ecstasy beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.98,1:02:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to get you to come out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.98,1:02:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that point,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.98,1:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you need somebody to know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.98,1:02:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is he blissed out or is he catatonic?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.98,1:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a psychiatrist or a guru, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.98,1:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think in the last book,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.36,1:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I described how you can tell the difference
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.36,1:03:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.36,1:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he in a divine state?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.36,1:03:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.36,1:03:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he catatonic?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.36,1:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.36,1:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you may get it the other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.94,1:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.19,1:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had several people tell me
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.19,1:03:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,they were higher than Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.19,1:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the kinesiology, they were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.19,1:03:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll repeat that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.19,1:03:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody has ever existed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.19,1:03:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,who's been higher than Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.19,1:03:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or Buddha or Krishna.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.19,1:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that tells you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.48,1:03:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that it has been or is higher than any of them
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.57,1:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is not coming from the right place.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.57,1:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Needs a psychiatrist, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.80,1:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Such things do occur.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.86,1:03:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.86,1:03:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,explain certain rather peculiar phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.86,1:03:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,why people are impressed by them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.86,1:03:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.86,1:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to justify such statements.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.88,1:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.88,1:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.88,1:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.88,1:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you ever hear it said to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.88,1:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,no,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.88,1:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you already know in your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.88,1:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.94,1:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the divination of spirits,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.59,1:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we would know that this is not of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.03,1:04:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.03,1:04:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are the only things
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.09,1:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make sure I'd said.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.09,1:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.19,1:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,now we just ask questions
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.19,1:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and go do sort of a spiritual free-for-all.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.19,1:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way the,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.19,1:04:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the way this is set up,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.19,1:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we're setting up the sound system
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.32,1:04:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so that everybody can hear this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.32,1:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do a little better
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.32,1:04:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and different than this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.65,1:04:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a different sound system today
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.65,1:04:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and we finally have it readjusted.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.65,1:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody will be able to hear the questions
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.65,1:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and hear the answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.65,1:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.65,1:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everybody to feel free
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.65,1:04:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to come up and ask anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.65,1:04:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll see what shows up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.65,1:04:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.90,1:04:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we're moving more towards the end of the year
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.90,1:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,where we said,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.90,1:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going to be more and more like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.90,1:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more spontaneous questions dialogue
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.90,1:05:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's actually what's on people's mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.26,1:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be in the photograph,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.26,1:05:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.26,1:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cover your face with a napkin.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.75,1:05:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be photographed with that dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.36,1:05:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.36,1:05:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,any photographs that are taken
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.36,1:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are just personal for our scrapbook.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.36,1:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing gets put out to the media.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.36,1:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just thought you'd like that reassurance
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.17,1:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will not appear on the internet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.40,1:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.84,1:05:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.84,1:05:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In a previous lecture,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.84,1:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you had made a statement that about 23% or 24% of the time
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.84,1:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.84,1:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you had cautioned people who were into extreme sports.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.84,1:05:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you elaborate on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.26,1:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Extreme sports?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.26,1:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm trying to get people used to...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.26,1:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, getting out of the Newtonian paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.30,1:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to move through quantum mechanics
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.30,1:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,where you don't have certainty,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.30,1:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you have probability and likelihoods.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.30,1:06:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood is
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.48,1:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if you make 32 high jumps with a five-gainer
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.05,1:06:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.05,1:06:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood, the certainty is not there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.38,1:06:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The 33rd jump, you can break your neck.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.38,1:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I gave an example right here in Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.53,1:06:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of nice guys that ran an animal place up there
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.01,1:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in the back of the Pizza Hut.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.01,1:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And they would...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.21,1:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When you called them,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.21,1:06:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they would come over and get the rattlesnakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.21,1:06:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were great.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.23,1:06:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, people are scared of rattlesnakes
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.23,1:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lot of this is becoming sort of suburban in a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.23,1:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So people just called them
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.23,1:06:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and they would come over and get the rattlesnake, no charge.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.23,1:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of them got bit 19 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.01,1:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rattlesnakes bit him 19 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.01,1:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the 20th time, he just assumed he was immune and he died.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.30,1:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was not.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.30,1:07:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I'm saying don't push your luck
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.30,1:07:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,based on the Newtonian paradigm of reality
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.30,1:07:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,because the Newtonian paradigm is not the total reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.55,1:07:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As we see from quantum mechanics and nonlinear dynamics,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.55,1:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what we're dealing with here is probability and likelihoods,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.55,1:07:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but not certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.86,1:07:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have that here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.86,1:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it too late to put that up?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.86,1:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the Newtonian paradigm?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.26,1:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put that up
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.26,1:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because I just wanted to see what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.26,1:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, once you begin to expand
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.26,1:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond the Newtonian paradigm of reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.23,1:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the Newtonian paradigm of form.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.23,1:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's decipherable by the differential calculus.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.46,1:07:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Isaac Newton was the source of the differential calculus.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.71,1:07:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates in about 460,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.00,1:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the same level as the idea of causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.00,1:08:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a world of certainty,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.57,1:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,linear certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.53,1:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certain because of the limitation of its own self-definition.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.59,1:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As you begin to move to the next higher level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.60,1:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,now you're dealing in quantum mechanics,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.60,1:08:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,quantum reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.60,1:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in the Newtonian,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.85,1:08:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,this causes this and there's an absolute certainty about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.85,1:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's only the macroscopic world.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.43,1:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In the microscopic world now,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.43,1:08:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of quantum mechanics,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.43,1:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,E equals MC squared,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.50,1:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you start going from
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.56,1:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the Schrodinger equations,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.56,1:08:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,time independent and time dependent.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.56,1:08:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going through the Heisenberg principle.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.56,1:08:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ending up with the Dirac conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.56,1:08:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And through the von Neumann processes,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.56,1:08:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A or B, one or two,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.56,1:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what you have now is you don't have certainty
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.77,1:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,at the submicroscopic level.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.77,1:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have probability.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.77,1:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we talk in spiritual language
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.77,1:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about the influence of the field,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.77,1:09:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're talking about now
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.77,1:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is not causality on a one-to-one linear basis,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.77,1:09:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.77,1:09:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say if you have a drinking problem,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.77,1:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if you just go to AA and sit in the room,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.77,1:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the field begins to alter your thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.77,1:09:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a predictable world.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.14,1:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is the way the world is,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.14,1:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,after 19 rattlesnake bites,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.47,1:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd be okay on the 20th.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.47,1:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't the way the world is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.47,1:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way the world is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.47,1:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.47,1:09:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely that 19 out of 20 times,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.47,1:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the 20th time you'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.78,1:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in the quantum mechanics,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.78,1:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,this linear certainty is beginning to loosen up
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.78,1:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,now a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.78,1:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 100 times out of 100 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.78,1:10:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 99.9% out of 100 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.92,1:10:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you begin to see disorderly, illogical,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.92,1:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,unpredictable, free, creative.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.92,1:10:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got space for free will.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.01,1:10:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is Newtonian,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.01,1:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be no karmic merit in any decision
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.01,1:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because this caused you to think this way,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.01,1:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that caused you to think this way,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.01,1:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what caused you to make this conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.01,1:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No room for karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.01,1:10:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No spiritual freedom.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.13,1:10:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be room for the unpredictable,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.13,1:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the illogical, to be free, to be creative,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.13,1:10:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,imaginative, progressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.13,1:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this field is diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.13,1:10:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.13,1:10:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not causal.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.31,1:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not local.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.07,1:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is provable.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.07,1:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is comprehensible,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.07,1:10:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but not provable.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.35,1:10:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I get oddball letters all the time from people
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.35,1:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that get lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.61,1:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They miss what the whole book's about,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.61,1:10:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and they start to argue with the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.61,1:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,mathematical analogies that I make.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.61,1:11:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I made it quite explicit.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.61,1:11:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,These are just analogous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.61,1:11:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not literal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.61,1:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And they start to argue about provability.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.61,1:11:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't actually prove anything
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.68,1:11:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,any time except something that you mentalize.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.68,1:11:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in reality can be proven.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.68,1:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's called provable is a mentalization.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.03,1:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's provable within a structured mentalization.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.17,1:11:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not provable within the world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.17,1:11:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because causality doesn't exist within the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.17,1:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so you couldn't prove it because it isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.17,1:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a conception.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.28,1:11:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can comprehend it,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.28,1:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but you cannot prove it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.28,1:11:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's observable.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.28,1:11:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is simultaneous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.28,1:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Past, present, and future are not sequential.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.28,1:11:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Newtonian paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.28,1:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that was yesterday, now is now,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.47,1:11:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.73,1:11:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In the microscopic world,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.73,1:12:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow has already happened,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.73,1:12:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and yesterday won't get here till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.85,1:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason everybody's here is because of their future.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.85,1:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They think they're propelled by their past.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.31,1:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,People are attracted because their future
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.31,1:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.31,1:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If your future hadn't been decided to become enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.50,1:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be no reason for your body
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.50,1:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to drag itself here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.22,1:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an electromagnet,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.22,1:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you're being pulled by the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.22,1:12:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not being propelled by the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.22,1:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The past is over already,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.06,1:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so where would it get the power to propel you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.06,1:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The past is already dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.80,1:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's dead,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.80,1:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,how would it be activating you in the present?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.80,1:12:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.56,1:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We said time-dependent and time-independent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.56,1:12:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the two Schrodinger equations.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.63,1:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stochastic meaning unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.63,1:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.63,1:12:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, it's altered by observation.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.63,1:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Heisenberg principle.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.63,1:13:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As we explained before,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.61,1:13:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Einstein calibrates at 499.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.77,1:13:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where he bucked.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.17,1:13:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He bucked right here because he said,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.22,1:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,after the Copenhagen Convention,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.22,1:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he said,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.22,1:13:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer to think that there is an independent,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.22,1:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,objective universe independent of human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.22,1:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the Heisenberg principle
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.56,1:13:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,forces you to a metaphysical,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.61,1:13:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophic shift,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.61,1:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole basis of science,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.61,1:13:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and it requires a shift of paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.93,1:13:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At calibration level 500,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.93,1:13:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you move from the literal,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.93,1:13:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,provable Newtonian paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.93,1:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,into the non-provable subjectivity
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.93,1:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.93,1:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And Einstein just refused to go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.77,1:13:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He refused to go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.06,1:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, he was quite religious.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.06,1:14:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite religious, and yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.28,1:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,not yet ready to make a paradigm jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.60,1:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is a reality
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.60,1:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that is not objective, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.85,1:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but subjective.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.85,1:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this then becomes unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.60,1:14:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You see possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.60,1:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the fact that
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.60,1:14:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's altered by observation,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.60,1:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing that intervenes,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.60,1:14:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,intervenes in the two,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.60,1:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,between the Schroeder and the Dirac equation,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.60,1:14:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Heisenberg principle of observation.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.60,1:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've really looked at it,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.60,1:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,once human consciousness has touched it,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.60,1:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's already changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.60,1:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.60,1:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've collapsed the wave function.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.63,1:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you've collapsed the wave function,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.63,1:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you have altered
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.63,1:14:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective consciousness of all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.21,1:14:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time everybody here says yes
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.21,1:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to something that's integrous
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.21,1:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and no to something that's not integrous,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.21,1:14:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you've made it more and more difficult
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.21,1:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for the non-integrous
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.21,1:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.27,1:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the field, as it moves from 190
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.27,1:15:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,back in 1980,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.27,1:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly shifted to 207.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.27,1:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The total field of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.59,1:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,will not tolerate now
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.59,1:15:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,things that it tolerated when I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.59,1:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grew up,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.77,1:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if you didn't get their money,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.77,1:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody else will.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.77,1:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.77,1:15:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get their money,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.77,1:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't get them,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.77,1:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody else will.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.77,1:15:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, this is not integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.77,1:15:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this old farmer's
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.77,1:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,never going to get his money back
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.77,1:15:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the peanut vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.77,1:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, if you don't get their money,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.14,1:15:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody else will.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.52,1:15:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That went back in the 50s
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.52,1:15:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or whenever that time was.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.86,1:15:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.86,1:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't go now
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.86,1:15:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because after Enron and all that
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.86,1:15:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and Martha Stewart and all,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.86,1:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,people now see that integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.86,1:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you're going to be nailed up there for,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.86,1:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,friends, not profit, integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.86,1:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they made plenty of profit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.86,1:15:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They should have been
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.86,1:15:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a Fifth Avenue ticker-tape parade for them,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.86,1:15:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,these guys that made billions
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.86,1:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the investors.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.89,1:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, their heads rolled.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.89,1:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the world has shifted.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.89,1:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, every time we are integrous,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.89,1:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we increase the likelihood that integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.89,1:16:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood that integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.97,1:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to be continued.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.85,1:16:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can see you're dealing with uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.85,1:16:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and, of course, the difference is
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.85,1:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you're dealing with power.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.85,1:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you're dealing with force.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.85,1:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you're dealing with content.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.85,1:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you're dealing with context.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.85,1:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the context,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.85,1:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the field out of which the power is coming,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.85,1:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the content or form.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.85,1:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.50,1:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,all spiritually evolved people
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.50,1:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or spiritually committed people
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.50,1:16:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by the sheer commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.50,1:16:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is they are already in the process
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.50,1:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of changing the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.50,1:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People say,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.50,1:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what can I do to change the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.50,1:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell them, stay out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.76,1:16:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers, stay out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.76,1:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing a lot for the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.76,1:16:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventy-eight percent of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.76,1:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is doing otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.76,1:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,not doing what they can for each other
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.76,1:16:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or for the world, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.76,1:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I try to teach the girls
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.76,1:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that the girls aren't, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.76,1:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one little smile
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.76,1:17:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,will change somebody else's whole day.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.76,1:17:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.89,1:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to be surrounded by love,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.89,1:17:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all you have to do
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.89,1:17:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is acknowledge people
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.89,1:17:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as you walk through the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.89,1:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you say thank you,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.02,1:17:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the telephone operator,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.02,1:17:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, boy, you really took that order.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.02,1:17:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That was terrific.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.02,1:17:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just hear them light up.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.02,1:17:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They just light up.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.07,1:17:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they're sort of like the dog, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.34,1:17:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When you give it a pat,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.34,1:17:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody just blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.34,1:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.34,1:17:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why New York
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.34,1:17:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is a wonderful and friendly place.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.34,1:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as you smile,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.34,1:17:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,literally walking down the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.34,1:17:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they just go,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.34,1:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that little flower just blossoms,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.35,1:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and you become part of the conditions
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.35,1:17:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,which allow them to blossom.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.35,1:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so that sort of cuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.38,1:17:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you asked that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.38,1:17:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.38,1:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll shut this off.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.69,1:17:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she's sorry she asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.69,1:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.30,1:17:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Next question.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.53,1:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As a participant in the health field,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.77,1:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and being in a very evidence-based period,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.77,1:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,am I adding negatively
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.77,1:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to the collective unconscious effect
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.77,1:18:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,on disease process?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.77,1:18:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.77,1:18:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm making wrong assumptions,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.77,1:18:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but my understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.77,1:18:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of the collective unconscious
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.77,1:18:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,on disease processes
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.81,1:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is that our diseases,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.81,1:18:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.81,1:18:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,are the result of the collective unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.81,1:18:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, certainly,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.81,1:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind of disease that we're dealing with
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.81,1:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the disease that we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.81,1:18:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the disease that we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.81,1:18:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly the kind of disease that we see.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.81,1:18:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the miracle says,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.81,1:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you're subject to what you hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.81,1:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you think smoking's gonna kill you,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.81,1:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I advise you not to smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.81,1:18:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have stopped smoking, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.35,1:18:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.35,1:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.35,1:18:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't started.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.35,1:18:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll go on to the next person.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.35,1:18:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.35,1:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,because you had a couple questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.35,1:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get another.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.35,1:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,People ask that question, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.35,1:19:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're subject to what you hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.82,1:19:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you may have already answered this,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.85,1:19:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.85,1:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's time to leave, you leave,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.85,1:19:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and many people with pure lungs
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.78,1:19:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,leave this planet every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.53,1:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If bad lungs don't get you out,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.53,1:19:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,karma will find another way,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.53,1:19:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a CVA or a stroke or, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.53,1:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the moment arrives,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.06,1:19:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you will not be here afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.06,1:19:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you may have already answered this,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.06,1:19:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but if in amongst all those ego messages
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.06,1:19:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there is this sensation
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.06,1:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of wanting to transcend that,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.06,1:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that can't be coming,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.25,1:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that message of wanting to transcend the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.25,1:19:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,can't be coming from the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.25,1:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is that coming from...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.25,1:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.25,1:19:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.43,1:19:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, like a field of gravity,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.43,1:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,this field is like attracting,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.43,1:20:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,pulling us towards it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.69,1:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And meantime, the ego is struggling
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.97,1:20:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to prevent that from happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.97,1:20:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.97,1:20:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as you transcend it,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.97,1:20:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the death of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.97,1:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.97,1:20:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.97,1:20:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it loses its grip on mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.10,1:20:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as you try to move up,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.10,1:20:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it tries to counter it, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.10,1:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,tries to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.10,1:20:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.19,1:20:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you understand it,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.19,1:20:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the weaker it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.19,1:20:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.19,1:20:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See, it's not operating in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.64,1:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And light and dark are not opposites.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.02,1:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.02,1:20:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as you hold the light on something,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.02,1:20:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the darkness disappears.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.02,1:20:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.02,1:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because darkness is not the opposite of light,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.02,1:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it merely is its absence.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.02,1:20:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the calibrated scale of consciousness then,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.22,1:20:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the degree to which divinity and love predominate
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.22,1:20:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is why the calibrations are high.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.34,1:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The more it tends...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.34,1:21:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The more the light goes down,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.34,1:21:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the more towards darkness,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.34,1:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the lower end of the scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.34,1:21:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're not opposites.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.34,1:21:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The top is not the opposite of the bottom of the scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.34,1:21:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's just a gradation.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.34,1:21:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, every conscious decision we make then
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.34,1:21:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,moves us up and down in the water,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.34,1:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,like little quarks, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.34,1:21:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I always figured like little quarks
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.34,1:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with little things like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.34,1:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we go this way,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.34,1:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the quark goes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.34,1:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we go this way,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.34,1:21:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the quark goes down.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.34,1:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.34,1:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.34,1:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's making those choices?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.34,1:21:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the field making those choices,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.34,1:21:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,this desire to transcend,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.34,1:21:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it the ego making the choices?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.34,1:21:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.34,1:21:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirit's making the choices.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.34,1:21:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.34,1:21:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a health-related question, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.34,1:21:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If the goal is to completely surrender,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.47,1:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,as you were talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.47,1:21:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were going through
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.47,1:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the 12 steps,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.47,1:21:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,then aren't efforts of searching around,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.47,1:21:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for healing kind of things
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.47,1:21:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of resisting that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.47,1:21:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Resisting having completely surrendered,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.47,1:21:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if it is in my karma
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.47,1:22:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a particular physical condition?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.47,1:22:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's sort of an ambiguous question
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.47,1:22:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because the intention to get well
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.47,1:22:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,would lead you to seek out the means to do so,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.47,1:22:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which would be the natural thing to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.47,1:22:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to completely,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.63,1:22:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,totally surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.63,1:22:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and allow it to be however it is
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.63,1:22:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,would be a different level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.63,1:22:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And a higher level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.92,1:22:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it persists or does not persist,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.92,1:22:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.92,1:22:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.92,1:22:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a choice,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.92,1:22:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.92,1:22:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at this level is yes,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.92,1:22:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at this level is no,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.92,1:22:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at this level is yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.92,1:22:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to know in what context,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.92,1:22:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.92,1:22:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're arriving at this decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.92,1:22:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because at one level,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.05,1:22:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't make any difference
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.05,1:22:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you live or you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.05,1:22:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.05,1:22:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.07,1:22:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's how it seems from that level.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.07,1:22:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.07,1:22:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But it makes a difference to whom,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.07,1:22:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you live or die,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.07,1:22:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.27,1:22:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So one constantly chooses life
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.27,1:23:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in whatever form it may express itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.27,1:23:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,including the non-physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.27,1:23:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.27,1:23:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it was time to leave the body, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.46,1:23:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And one function I used to have in the nursing home
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.46,1:23:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is I would say to some old lady
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.46,1:23:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with all these tubes stuck in her,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.46,1:23:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and she'd be going up and down the wheelchair,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.46,1:23:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.46,1:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,help,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.46,1:23:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,help,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.77,1:23:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,help,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.77,1:23:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,help.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.77,1:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're putting more tubes in her
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.77,1:23:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and more things,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.77,1:23:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and she must need more narcotics.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.77,1:23:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.77,1:23:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you want help with?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.77,1:23:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She said,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.77,1:23:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,let me go,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.77,1:23:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.77,1:23:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody lets her die.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.77,1:23:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's against Medicare rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.77,1:23:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know it's against Medicare rules
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.77,1:23:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to let anybody die?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.77,1:23:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.64,1:23:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.64,1:23:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's against Medicare rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.64,1:23:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's illegal to let anybody die.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.64,1:23:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The most natural thing in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.64,1:23:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to get born,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.64,1:23:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to die,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.64,1:23:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the two things that are inevitable,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.64,1:23:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is against the Medicare rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.64,1:23:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What she means by help is let me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.25,1:23:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't let me die.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.78,1:23:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the natural end of life?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.78,1:23:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The natural end of life
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.78,1:24:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is you reach a certain feeling of inevitability.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.78,1:24:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that point,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.78,1:24:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you have no interest in eating anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.78,1:24:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The natural way to leave the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.78,1:24:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is to realize that and to stop eating.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.78,1:24:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nature's way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.78,1:24:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When the animal gets sick enough,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.78,1:24:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes off,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.78,1:24:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it wants solitude,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.78,1:24:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it wants to stop eating,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.78,1:24:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and be left alone in peace
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.78,1:24:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to slowly let itself out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.78,1:24:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And this poor old lady is pleading for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.78,1:24:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put me somewhere in the corner
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.78,1:24:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave me alone
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.78,1:24:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop trying to hydrate me,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.94,1:24:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,tube feed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.94,1:24:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.94,1:24:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and let nature take its course.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.94,1:24:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The natural way to leave is to stop eating.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.94,1:24:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.14,1:24:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If anybody says they want to die and commit suicide,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.21,1:24:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.21,1:24:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how was lunch?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.21,1:24:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.21,1:24:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.92,1:24:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working on,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.92,1:25:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.92,1:25:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on spiritual realization for the last three years,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.92,1:25:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have gotten to the point
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.92,1:25:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that I understand that there is no causal,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.92,1:25:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that it isn't my past.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.92,1:25:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't blame anyone or anything that happened,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.92,1:25:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I do see the unfolding and the blossoming.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.92,1:25:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I start thinking about the past,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.92,1:25:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes I don't think about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.92,1:25:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I do,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.92,1:25:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to kind of think
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.92,1:25:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've really firmly put it behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.92,1:25:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But in your last book,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.92,1:25:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that it can be an advantage
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.92,1:25:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to have past life regression
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.92,1:25:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to find out what the karmic residual is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.92,1:25:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that is causing the things to happen in your life
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.92,1:25:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you better understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.92,1:25:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're up against a block,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.92,1:25:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,a block,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.18,1:25:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't seem to overcome it,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.68,1:25:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you try prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.68,1:25:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you try everything,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.90,1:25:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.90,1:25:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it's usually something specific.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.93,1:25:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And, yeah, past life recall,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.93,1:25:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,past life regression can sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.93,1:25:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,well, sometimes take it right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.93,1:25:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's very simple techniques,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.93,1:26:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,just self-hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.93,1:26:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You get off at floor 18,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.93,1:26:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.93,1:26:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden the movie starts,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.93,1:26:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and only it's you in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.93,1:26:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's quite obvious now
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.93,1:26:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,what the whole story is about,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.93,1:26:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you suspected is not only so,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.93,1:26:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's very, very so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.93,1:26:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And each of those lifetimes,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.93,1:26:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if you do past life regression,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.93,1:26:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as you come to in that lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.93,1:26:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it's always you that's there.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.93,1:26:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you had experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.93,1:26:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same me each time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.93,1:26:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is, a blacksmith.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.03,1:26:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In that lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.03,1:26:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he's got huge muscles like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.03,1:26:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's got an apron,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.03,1:26:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's a very powerful guy,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.03,1:26:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a very strong guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.22,1:26:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So each lifetime that one recalls.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.22,1:26:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's only certain critical ones
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.22,1:26:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that are of any, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.22,1:26:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.42,1:26:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that tend to come in people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.42,1:26:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it sometimes solves self-possession,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.42,1:26:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,self-pity.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.42,1:26:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.48,1:26:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why this pattern?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.48,1:26:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the usual answer is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.48,1:26:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's exactly, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.48,1:27:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you're playing the other role now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.57,1:27:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And many a person says, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.57,1:27:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have been an SOB in another lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.68,1:27:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you, that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.68,1:27:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were an SOB in other lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.68,1:27:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing I would like to say
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.68,1:27:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is about the 12 steps I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.68,1:27:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an alcoholic,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.68,1:27:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I did use the 12 steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.68,1:27:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of the things that,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.68,1:27:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I did stop drinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.68,1:27:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very thankful to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.68,1:27:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was very much giving over
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.68,1:27:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the idea that I had no power over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.68,1:27:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I basically answered my own question
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.68,1:27:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that what you were going through
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.68,1:27:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is that all I have to do now
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.68,1:27:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is surrender the rest of the blocks to,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.68,1:27:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to continue that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.47,1:27:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I stopped 15 years ago
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.47,1:27:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,when I stopped drinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.47,1:27:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped to continually take that inventory.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.47,1:27:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think now that if I just more surrender myself
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.47,1:27:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to the idea,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.47,1:27:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have to go through the past life regression.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.47,1:27:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.47,1:27:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.47,1:27:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if they have,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.47,1:28:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if they belong to something like AA,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.47,1:28:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,where the sobriety indicates sort of an endpoint,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.47,1:28:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,then they may just maintain the program.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.47,1:28:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Bill Wilson, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.67,1:28:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,said that the AAs don't really realize
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.67,1:28:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that the 12 steps,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.67,1:28:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that sobriety is just the,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.67,1:28:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,jacks for openers.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.67,1:28:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's jacks for openers.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.67,1:28:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You do the steps, you get sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.67,1:28:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And most people think,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.67,1:28:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I'm done now.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.67,1:28:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, no,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.67,1:28:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what leads to the great discoveries
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.67,1:28:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the great spiritual growth and experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.25,1:28:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So he used to think that was maybe an error
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.53,1:28:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that they should not have indicated
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.53,1:28:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that sobriety itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.53,1:28:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,although I think for practical reasons,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.53,1:28:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's good enough for this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.53,1:28:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing one excellent job today.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.53,1:28:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to do a wrestling point
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.53,1:28:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for a lifetime or two
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.53,1:29:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then start up your momentum again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.13,1:29:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of a follow-up to that is,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.06,1:29:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,could you expand a little more
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.06,1:29:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,on a technique for accessing previous lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.06,1:29:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do past life regression.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.31,1:29:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's a very simple thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.31,1:29:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.43,1:29:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You just do self-hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.43,1:29:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.43,1:29:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.81,1:29:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.81,1:29:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got to go learn self-hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.81,1:29:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to ask,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.81,1:29:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,what is your motivation?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.81,1:29:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it worth?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.81,1:29:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it may be.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.81,1:29:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And first of all,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.81,1:29:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize that one is at a certain point
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.05,1:29:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in a continuum of an endless series,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.05,1:29:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,an endless life, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.05,1:29:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just one life.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.05,1:29:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's these various chapters and episodes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.05,1:29:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one you dip into the physicality
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.05,1:29:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as a very definite karmic purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.05,1:29:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it quite clearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.05,1:29:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the next lesson comes around.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.05,1:29:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a certain benefit to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.05,1:29:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's people who have written books on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.05,1:30:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're accessible.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.05,1:30:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the names of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.05,1:30:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's primarily self-hypnosis
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.05,1:30:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and then your intention, intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.05,1:30:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold in mind a certain intentionality
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.05,1:30:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and you walk down the dark steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.18,1:30:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you take the elevator
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.18,1:30:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and you find your answer on level eight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.18,1:30:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You get off the elevator
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.18,1:30:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the whole lifetime begins,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.18,1:30:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.27,1:30:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you're watching a movie
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.27,1:30:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where that's happening there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.27,1:30:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the movie
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.27,1:30:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything moves around you as it did.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.27,1:30:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're, I mean, the self is there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.93,1:30:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very much like out-of-body experience
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.93,1:30:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you go out of body.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.84,1:30:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very much you that's out of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.84,1:30:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The physicality is there,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.84,1:30:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but the you is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.84,1:30:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And in fact, there's techniques
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.06,1:30:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,using out-of-body experience
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.06,1:30:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for karmic research.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.06,1:30:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you go in realms
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.06,1:30:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,where there is no past, present, or future
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.06,1:31:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and you merely go back and visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.06,1:31:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.77,1:31:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wrote Journeys Out of the Body?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.77,1:31:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Monroe, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.47,1:31:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Monroe Institute.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.47,1:31:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Various places like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.47,1:31:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So with a little inquiry,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.47,1:31:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you can find places that specialize
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.47,1:31:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in past life recall
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.47,1:31:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and various techniques,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.47,1:31:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hypnosis, out-of-body experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.47,1:31:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.47,1:31:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My 2% is very active.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.47,1:31:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.51,1:31:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I keep getting to this point
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.51,1:31:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,where I think,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.51,1:31:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,why isn't this just maybe
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.51,1:31:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate ego trick, all this,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.51,1:31:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we're all experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.51,1:31:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the same ultimate ego trick?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.51,1:31:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is a psychiatric problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.06,1:31:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go sit on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.06,1:31:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer comes to you
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.06,1:31:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,just out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.06,1:31:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're looking somewhat,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.22,1:31:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like you're pressing the linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.22,1:32:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to press logic, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.22,1:32:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not going to work
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.22,1:32:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in the spiritual domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.22,1:32:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more your intention to know,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.22,1:32:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,your prayer and dedication, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.22,1:32:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,will finesse.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.22,1:32:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.22,1:32:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.22,1:32:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you cause things to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.22,1:32:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the spiritual paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.22,1:32:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more like you finesse them.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.22,1:32:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Through prayer and meditation,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.27,1:32:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you increase the likelihood
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.27,1:32:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that when you get your gas
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.75,1:32:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,at the next station,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.75,1:32:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the guy giving you the change says,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.75,1:32:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and by the way, so-and-so,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.75,1:32:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's just what you're asking for.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.75,1:32:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to be open
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.75,1:32:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to hear the answer to the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.75,1:32:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'll come through, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.06,1:32:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and just sit next to somebody on a bus,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.06,1:32:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and he looks from this paper,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.06,1:32:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says, yackety-yack,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.06,1:32:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and man, that's just what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.06,1:32:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you give the universe a chance
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.97,1:32:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to respond to your question.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.97,1:32:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't look for a linear cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.00,1:32:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because once you pose the question out there,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.00,1:33:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the answer will come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.81,1:33:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somebody will just walk up to you
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.81,1:33:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, yackety-yack,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.81,1:33:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say, whoa, hey, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.14,1:33:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.52,1:33:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So when people say they're praying for me,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.52,1:33:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,should I worry about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.52,1:33:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.90,1:33:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So really, what is prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.90,1:33:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or how would we best pray?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.97,1:33:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, prayer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.97,1:33:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, through devotion and dedication,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.22,1:33:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,one's commitment to God becomes quite intense.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.22,1:33:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, in the 12 steps,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.97,1:33:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it addresses prayer directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.97,1:33:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sought through prayer and meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.97,1:33:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase our conscious contact with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.97,1:33:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're like permitting,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.02,1:33:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you're taking,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.02,1:34:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, the ego is very much yang,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.15,1:34:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,papo,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.15,1:34:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and the spirit is very much yin,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.89,1:34:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.09,1:34:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's hard for those who live in a world
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.47,1:34:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of the harder you push,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.47,1:34:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the harder you try,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.47,1:34:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater you bring home the bacon, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.78,1:34:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So spiritual work is more like yin,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.10,1:34:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you get out of the way of it
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.10,1:34:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and you float back with it,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.46,1:34:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the answer comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.01,1:34:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes to you out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.01,1:34:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer came out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.22,1:34:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the other day driving along.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.22,1:34:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, what's the best way
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.35,1:34:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to present a certain piece of material?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.35,1:34:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it was just obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.35,1:34:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not question and answer, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.57,1:34:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I posed the question at breakfast
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.82,1:34:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and at noon I'm driving along
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.82,1:34:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the answer just revealed itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.82,1:34:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you learn how to finesse using yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.85,1:35:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So the power of yin is equal to the power of yang.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.85,1:35:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get the publicity.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.35,1:35:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuclear submarines get the publicity.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.55,1:35:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the power of yin that summons forth
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.55,1:35:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is needed for survival, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.55,1:35:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the power of prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.51,1:35:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it summons to itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.60,1:35:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,summons, attracts to itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.60,1:35:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any such thing
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.93,1:35:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as praying for another person?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.93,1:35:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.60,1:35:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,People pray for each other all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.60,1:35:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, please let them see the right way to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.39,1:35:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We all, we pray that God's will be done, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.97,1:35:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That God's will be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.97,1:35:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask for what is God's intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.97,1:36:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because if a person is going through a karmic lesson
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.18,1:36:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and you want to interfere with the karmic lesson,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.18,1:36:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, you're destroying the person's spiritual integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.18,1:36:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.18,1:36:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So if people get sober because you have them arrested and jailed
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.18,1:36:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and put in prison and then into a forced program,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.18,1:36:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there's really no karmic benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.59,1:36:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't said yes to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.61,1:36:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.61,1:36:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It did not come of his own volition through his own surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.61,1:36:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So that sobriety will last till he gets out of jail, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.61,1:36:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and on the way home it'll disappear because it's forced.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.65,1:36:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.65,1:36:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first step in the Al-Anon program, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.65,1:36:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is in a way saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.65,1:36:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,don't try to rob others of karmic merit
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.65,1:36:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,by acting, you know, in what you think is their best interest
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.65,1:36:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,using force and coercion.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.65,1:36:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it's saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.51,1:36:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow people to derive the karmic benefit
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.51,1:36:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes only from saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.51,1:36:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.51,1:36:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask God for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.51,1:37:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I ask God for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.27,1:37:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a totally different thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.27,1:37:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.39,1:37:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.64,1:37:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people that are forced to, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.64,1:37:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,discontinue certain behaviors may also shift later on
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.81,1:37:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and now do it by agreement and understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.81,1:37:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe they're forced to go there by the court,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.81,1:37:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and then much to their surprise,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.81,1:37:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they become enthusiastic about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.86,1:37:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question that I'm having a little bit of problems wording it,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.65,1:37:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think you'll pick up real quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.65,1:37:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout the history of mankind or humankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.72,1:37:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we have avatars and the great enlightened ones,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.81,1:37:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna, Buddha, Jesus, as you've mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.81,1:37:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I would assume that there have been females
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.81,1:37:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that have reached these levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.81,1:37:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.81,1:38:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is politicizing it, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.63,1:38:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the reason I was asking, no, my thinking is,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.63,1:38:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was that perhaps there were,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.63,1:38:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but because of the nature of the civilization,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.63,1:38:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they weren't recognized.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.78,1:38:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to detect it,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.27,1:38:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but the minute I am, I will announce it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.55,1:38:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The other question was,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.55,1:38:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,going through the dark night of the soul,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.73,1:38:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,which you relate to about the agony,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.73,1:38:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotional and mental agony,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.73,1:38:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,how does one discern that between an ego conniption fit?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.18,1:38:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the ego can take you places.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.72,1:38:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One is transformative and the other is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.72,1:38:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The dark night of the soul takes you to,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.97,1:39:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the resolution to it is a spiritual experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.51,1:39:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,without which that likely would not have happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.53,1:39:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've answered my question, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.14,1:39:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The question about men and women,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.14,1:39:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as being God,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.53,1:39:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the question, because we've asked it,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.92,1:39:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to do with the strength of the nervous system,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.23,1:39:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that to go over 600, to go over 700 especially,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.23,1:39:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely difficult for the human nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.97,1:39:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we got is,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.97,1:39:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the only reason that men go the whole way,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.17,1:39:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,statistically more than women,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.17,1:39:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is because the nervous system
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.17,1:39:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is sufficiently strong to handle.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.17,1:39:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I got.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.17,1:39:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I bet you're going through childbirth,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.17,1:39:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that women don't have an equal...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.17,1:39:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so glad I wasn't born a woman, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.17,1:39:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They go through and survive a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.17,1:40:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think we can ask it again,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.17,1:40:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has nothing to do with gender.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.17,1:40:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.17,1:40:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer I give is permitted.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.17,1:40:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer I give is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.17,1:40:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only because of the nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.17,1:40:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For the same reason,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.17,1:40:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,moving rocks is usually given to men to do,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.17,1:40:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than women, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.17,1:40:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.17,1:40:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.17,1:40:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.17,1:40:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm live.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.17,1:40:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk, and we all are aware of Mother Teresa
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.17,1:40:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the tremendous ability that she had to do what she did.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.17,1:40:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just thought, perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.30,1:40:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe there's some other females in history
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.30,1:40:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm not aware of.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.30,1:40:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a great many Christian saints.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.30,1:40:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, Saint Teresa of Avila,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.30,1:40:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,many...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.30,1:40:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Many Christian saints that were women.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.68,1:40:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, in our lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.68,1:40:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother Teresa calibrates over 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.68,1:40:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's about as good as you can get on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.89,1:40:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarely, rarely ever does calibration ever go over 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.97,1:41:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it does, you don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.97,1:41:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, as each level is reached,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.97,1:41:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't hear from them.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.97,1:41:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600, you won't hear from...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.97,1:41:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,50% of them are going to leave,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.97,1:41:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't have to breathe,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.97,1:41:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.97,1:41:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize that...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.97,1:41:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reality...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.97,1:41:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the point of, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.97,1:41:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to please your relatives breathing this body again?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.97,1:41:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So 50% of the time, they don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.15,1:41:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then as you get higher to the 700s or 800s,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.15,1:41:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hardly any of them come back in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.15,1:41:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you get beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.64,1:41:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's once in a number of centuries
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.64,1:41:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that anybody will persist.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.64,1:41:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.64,1:41:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Women are smart enough they don't come back
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.64,1:41:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as often as men do.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.64,1:41:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They got the brains to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.06,1:41:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't disagree with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.89,1:41:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're too smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.89,1:41:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who needs this?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.89,1:42:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.72,1:42:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.92,1:42:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have the answers to these questions,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.36,1:42:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but I also think I might be intellectualizing,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.36,1:42:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's why I want to present this to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.36,1:42:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, am an ex-drunk,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.36,1:42:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I work the steps,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.36,1:42:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and amazing things happen as a result.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.36,1:42:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I listened to your tape
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.36,1:42:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,on alcoholism and consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.36,1:42:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I understood you correctly,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.36,1:42:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,your theory behind that was
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.36,1:42:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for those of us that are alcoholic,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.65,1:42:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason why we drink
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.65,1:42:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we're actually addicted
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.65,1:42:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to the God experience that we get through alcohol,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.65,1:42:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because alcohol or the drug
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.65,1:42:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of pushes the ego out of the way
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.65,1:42:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that's blocking it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.65,1:42:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You sedate the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.72,1:42:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get to feel the euphoria,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.72,1:42:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the euphoria is really the...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.72,1:42:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.72,1:42:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're sensing now,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.72,1:42:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because the block to it has been sedated.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.81,1:42:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're addicted to,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.32,1:42:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not addicted to the drug,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.32,1:43:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you're addicted to
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.57,1:43:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that wonderful state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.57,1:43:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What you've experienced
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.22,1:43:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're never satisfied with any less.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.43,1:43:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it that those of us that become alcoholic,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.43,1:43:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,do we perceive that
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.43,1:43:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,state of drunkenness differently
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.43,1:43:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,than those that don't?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.43,1:43:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I would think if everybody got that after a few drinks,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.43,1:43:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or is that a karmic thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.76,1:43:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody is a drunk,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.97,1:43:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they just haven't drunk enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.14,1:43:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have another lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.14,1:43:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,or two out at sea,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.14,1:43:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and by golly,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.19,1:43:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we used to hang out in the dives in the front,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.19,1:43:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and by golly, we had friendship,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.19,1:43:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and we hugged each other,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.19,1:43:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and we got boffed to the gills,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.19,1:43:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and we had fraternal love, you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.19,1:43:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and camaraderie, we didn't feel lonely,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.19,1:43:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't feel fear,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.19,1:43:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we felt fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.30,1:43:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now why wouldn't anybody in their right mind
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.30,1:44:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,want to repeat that?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.30,1:44:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I never could figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.30,1:44:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So ultimately,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.46,1:44:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,does that have to do with just the karma
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.46,1:44:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and where your soul is in its evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.46,1:44:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in that particular lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.46,1:44:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it has to do with a number of factors,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.46,1:44:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,physiologic and karmic,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.48,1:44:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and many of the people that,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.48,1:44:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ask with kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.48,1:44:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,how many lifetimes have they died of alcohol
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.48,1:44:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,before they finally got sober,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.48,1:44:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally the sixth time around they got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.57,1:44:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.57,1:44:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that have been in places like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.57,1:44:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in recovery groups,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.64,1:44:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of the fastest ways to God
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.64,1:44:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is to hit bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.64,1:44:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to get to God fast,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.00,1:44:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,give a guy a couple cases of whiskey
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.00,1:44:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.00,1:44:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.34,1:44:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.34,1:44:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.36,1:44:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we used to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.61,1:44:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, what can I do to my husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.61,1:44:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, send him another case of whiskey
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.61,1:44:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and he'll sit back and wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.19,1:45:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be happy to go to the recovery home.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.84,1:45:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The other question I had,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.84,1:45:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I may have misunderstood this,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.84,1:45:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was under the impression that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.84,1:45:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,people who have near-death experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.84,1:45:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,have a choice as to whether or not
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.84,1:45:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they want to come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.84,1:45:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true in that moment?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.84,1:45:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.84,1:45:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that's true,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.84,1:45:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then was that their time of death
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.63,1:45:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rest of the time after that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.63,1:45:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is like bonus time?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.43,1:45:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's punishment for not having left.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.23,1:45:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.23,1:45:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, things are not all that cut and dried.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.23,1:45:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, we want to differentiate
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.68,1:45:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,between near-death and out-of-body,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.68,1:45:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.68,1:45:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think everybody in our classes
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.01,1:45:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,are quite clear about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.01,1:45:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Out-of-body, there isn't such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.01,1:45:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Near-death is transformative.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.22,1:45:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And out-of-body, you calibrate the same
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.22,1:46:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,after as before,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.22,1:46:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which always seems surprising.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.26,1:46:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now that you realize you're a spirit,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.26,1:46:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems to me your consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.26,1:46:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is a little bit of a jump, but it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.61,1:46:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Near-death is quite something different.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.61,1:46:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Near-death
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.61,1:46:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is not exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.61,1:46:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's similar
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.61,1:46:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to illumination,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.61,1:46:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's a near-death
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.93,1:46:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of illumination.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.93,1:46:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an illumination that comes on spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.93,1:46:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.02,1:46:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be level 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.02,1:46:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One is more
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.69,1:46:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness to the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.69,1:46:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of whether or not this spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.69,1:46:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to re-enter this body or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.69,1:46:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Although love,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.69,1:46:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,can be the determining factor.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.69,1:46:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And several times,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.69,1:46:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially, it was love
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.69,1:46:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that decided
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.80,1:46:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to breathe it again,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.80,1:46:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,two or three times, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.82,1:46:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was love for somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.82,1:46:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who would view it as a big loss
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.82,1:46:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because they believe in death and all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.14,1:47:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And they would think you died.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.14,1:47:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So for their sake, you breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.27,1:47:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So the time of death that was determined
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.27,1:47:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,when the soul came into the body
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.27,1:47:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is the time when that choice is made
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.27,1:47:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,as to whether or not they're going to come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.27,1:47:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too detailed
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.27,1:47:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,a question. Whether in the near-death
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.27,1:47:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,experience you are represented
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.27,1:47:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,with an opportunity to reprogram
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.27,1:47:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the date of death
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.27,1:47:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,could be so, but I'd have to research
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.27,1:47:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,whether that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.40,1:47:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like you're given a chance
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.10,1:47:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to shift the
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.10,1:47:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,time date or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.10,1:47:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when it comes on,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.10,1:47:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact it came on as I walked down the aisle here
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.10,1:47:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,one time, there was
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.10,1:47:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the permission to leave that was very strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.10,1:47:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.10,1:47:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,magnet pulling it to
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.75,1:47:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,exquisite realms.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.17,1:47:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that experience you have
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.17,1:47:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness of complete and total
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.17,1:47:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,permission. You have permission,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.17,1:47:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute permission to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.17,1:47:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost an invitation to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.52,1:48:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And one doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.52,1:48:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what is going to happen out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.52,1:48:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If the body walked to the end and managed to
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.52,1:48:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,come back around the room, I guess that was the way
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.52,1:48:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it was going to go. And if it fell down,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.52,1:48:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it was going to fall down.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.52,1:48:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd say, would I keep on walking or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.52,1:48:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, keep on walking, and if you're dying
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.52,1:48:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then the body falls down, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.52,1:48:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it didn't fall down,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.52,1:48:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so I presume that was not the time to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.52,1:48:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.02,1:48:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I don't know though.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.02,1:48:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. A number of years ago
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.02,1:48:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the front door of the home
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.02,1:48:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,where I lived, and I tried to take a
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.02,1:48:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,left into my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.02,1:48:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And all at once, right here on the right side
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.02,1:48:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of my head, I heard a yellow note
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.02,1:48:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kitchen. And I tried to ignore it,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.02,1:48:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn left into my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.02,1:48:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard what? A yellow note
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.02,1:48:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kitchen. It was right
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.02,1:48:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,here, I could hear it. A yellow note?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.02,1:48:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the kitchen. What's a yellow note?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.02,1:48:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a yellow note?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.02,1:48:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just, I just heard the words
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.02,1:49:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,right here. I got into, I went through the front
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.02,1:49:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,door of my home, I tried to turn left
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.02,1:49:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,into my room. And all at
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.02,1:49:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,once, I heard the words,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.02,1:49:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a yellow note in
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.02,1:49:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the kitchen. And I heard it
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.02,1:49:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,from right here. So, I kept
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.02,1:49:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ignoring it, and three to four times,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.02,1:49:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to turn left,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.02,1:49:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was almost as if I couldn't turn
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.02,1:49:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,left into my room, I kept hearing
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.02,1:49:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the same thing. So,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.02,1:49:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided, I stood there alone and out loud,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.02,1:49:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, oh, alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.02,1:49:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I decided to
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.02,1:49:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,just walk into the kitchen to see what was
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.02,1:49:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,going on. So, I did,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.02,1:49:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I turned on the light, and on my
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.02,1:49:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,fruit bowl, there was a little yellow note
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.02,1:49:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,from my roommate, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.02,1:49:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It said, Crystal, your pineapple is ripe.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.02,1:49:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a yellow note
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.02,1:49:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kitchen. And then,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.02,1:49:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,last May, I awakened
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.02,1:49:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,one morning, and I wondered
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.02,1:49:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,what time it was. And I
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.02,1:49:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,heard, instead of on the right, I heard right
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.02,1:49:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of my head,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.02,1:49:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard, it's ten o'clock, in a
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.02,1:49:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,very clear voice. And I
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.02,1:50:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,thought to myself, oh no, it has to be eight or
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.02,1:50:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,nine. So, finally,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.02,1:50:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I put my head up, and I
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.02,1:50:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,looked down across the room, and I looked
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.02,1:50:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,at the clock, it was ten o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.02,1:50:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the question? The question
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.50,1:50:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is, where are these
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.50,1:50:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,things coming from? Why was I no
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.50,1:50:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,notified that there was a yellow note in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.50,1:50:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And why was I told it was ten o'clock
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.50,1:50:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when I couldn't visibly see it with my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.50,1:50:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, that's just your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.50,1:50:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's like out-of-body experience. Your
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.50,1:50:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,spirit can go all over the place and go back in the
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.50,1:50:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,body and report what's going on out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.50,1:50:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let me have one more question.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.50,1:50:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I used to go into a box.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.50,1:50:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you go to the Monroe Institute.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.59,1:50:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My spirit box. Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.59,1:50:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the things they teach you is how
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.59,1:50:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to, you know, astral projection
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.59,1:50:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and projection of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.59,1:50:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I remember the training itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.59,1:50:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ten-hour toilet was set around.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.59,1:50:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were supposed to project
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.68,1:50:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,your spirit into the box, read what's there,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.68,1:50:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and come back in, come back out again.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.77,1:50:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you go into the box, and it said,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.77,1:50:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,hello. And I came back, and I said, hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.77,1:51:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, yep, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.77,1:51:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can train
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.19,1:51:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself to do it at will.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.48,1:51:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My other question is, a number
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.48,1:51:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of years ago, I was with a friend in
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.48,1:51:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the living room in my apartment, and
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.48,1:51:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,almost at the same time, we both
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.48,1:51:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,perceived a screen of energy that was
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.48,1:51:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,right between us.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.48,1:51:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then a number of years after that,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.48,1:51:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sitting in someone else's living room
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.48,1:51:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to this person, and all at
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.48,1:51:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,once, it's as if, I guess, from the
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.48,1:51:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,third eye, all at once I perceived
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.48,1:51:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a being up in the corner of the
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.48,1:51:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,room, and
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.48,1:51:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that same screen of energy, which I had
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.48,1:51:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten about, was going across the room
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.48,1:51:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,behind the person I was talking to.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.48,1:51:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I've been told that you should
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.48,1:51:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,not be in contact with these
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.48,1:51:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,beings, and I've been told that
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.48,1:51:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you should. So I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.48,1:51:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,if that's right, or even why it
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.55,1:51:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,happened to me. I don't know anyone else
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.55,1:51:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,who has perceived that.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.55,1:51:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think these are spirits?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.55,1:51:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could see it. It was very different.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.55,1:51:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a different perception that opened up,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.55,1:52:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,as if you couldn't hear before, and then
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.55,1:52:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,all at once it was shocking, because it
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.55,1:52:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,just opened up, and then you didn't have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.55,1:52:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like clairvoyance, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.55,1:52:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have been. It was like an
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.55,1:52:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,altered state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.55,1:52:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't through my eyes, but it was
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.55,1:52:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,through here. It was in the corner, and
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.55,1:52:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the image was about this big, and it was waving its arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.55,1:52:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pointing to astral domains,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.73,1:52:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and various
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.81,1:52:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,entities that you meet there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.81,1:52:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can learn to do it at will.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.81,1:52:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My explanation is
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.81,1:52:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,correct. You're pointing to various
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.81,1:52:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,astral domains, and you can
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.81,1:52:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,train yourself to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.81,1:52:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you about the Menorah Institute. You can become
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.81,1:52:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,an expert at this, and travel all around
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.81,1:52:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the world, and
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.81,1:52:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,join the circus.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.81,1:52:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was going to get it for that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.81,1:52:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's because
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.81,1:52:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say the aura can be trained
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.81,1:52:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave at will,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.81,1:52:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and also to investigate
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.81,1:52:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,other domains.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.86,1:52:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was at Monroe,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.86,1:52:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked Bob Monroe. He had the most quiet,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.86,1:53:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.86,1:53:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You felt like you were in the presence of Jesus
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.86,1:53:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or something when he spoke. It was like a calmness.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.86,1:53:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't want you
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.86,1:53:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,getting into too many games out in the astral
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.86,1:53:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,domains, so he
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.86,1:53:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,trained you. You put on earphones,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.86,1:53:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and they
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.86,1:53:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,get picked up by the energy of the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.86,1:53:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,cross speed. Let's say you got
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.86,1:53:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a frequency at a certain
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.86,1:53:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,level in this ear, and a frequency level
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.86,1:53:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in this ear. He was an engineer,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.86,1:53:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a sound engineer.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.86,1:53:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're picking up is
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.86,1:53:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of the dissonance.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.86,1:53:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can train yourself to go
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.86,1:53:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,into consciousness state 10, 12,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.86,1:53:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,14, 15.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.86,1:53:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they went 10 to 15.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.86,1:53:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You go into an altered state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.51,1:53:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In an altered state of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.51,1:53:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you can leave the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.51,1:53:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,body and explore various realms.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.51,1:53:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a whistle.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.80,1:53:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hear this whistle,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.80,1:53:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you had to come back in the body and come home again.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.80,1:53:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People get involved
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.80,1:53:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in all kinds of adventures out in the astral
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.80,1:54:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,domains, all kinds of entities and
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.80,1:54:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,energies. They've got weird programs.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.80,1:54:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all kinds of places.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.80,1:54:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With training, you can get two or three of you
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.80,1:54:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can astral project together
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.80,1:54:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and decide where you're going to meet, what domain
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.80,1:54:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and what dimension and what point.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.80,1:54:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He had this whistle. Of course, we got
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.80,1:54:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,earphones on. You're out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.80,1:54:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,having various adventures and all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.80,1:54:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you hear this beep, beep, beep.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.80,1:54:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you've got to come back in the body. Bang!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.80,1:54:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You go back in the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.80,1:54:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just telling you it can be
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.53,1:54:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,trained.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.53,1:54:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be used
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.53,1:54:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for certain things.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.53,1:54:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the things it can be used for is
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.53,1:54:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,past life recall. You can actually
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.53,1:54:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,project yourself into that dimension,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.53,1:54:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,relive the exact experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.53,1:54:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.53,1:54:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people leave only
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.21,1:54:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,when they want and others will go out
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.21,1:54:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.52,1:54:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people have a hard time staying in their body.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.52,1:54:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the will
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.52,1:54:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to be there because they tend to drift off.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.52,1:55:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting in the dentist's
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.65,1:55:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,office, they go off.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.65,1:55:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other dimensions and other time frames
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.65,1:55:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dentist is waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.22,1:55:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.22,1:55:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're discovering what's possible
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.22,1:55:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,within the human psyche.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.85,1:55:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sort of an advancement
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.85,1:55:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because you start getting more evolved
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.85,1:55:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as you start becoming aware of those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.30,1:55:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro projecting dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.68,1:55:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.68,1:55:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,bring...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.68,1:55:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a level
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.68,1:55:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.68,1:55:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which was quite interesting
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.68,1:55:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to go through
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.68,1:55:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the so-called paranormal
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.68,1:55:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what classically call
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.68,1:55:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the cities, S-I-D-D-H-I-S
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.68,1:55:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly call them powers.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.01,1:55:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not actually powers
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.01,1:55:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but you become clairvoyant.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.01,1:56:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a clairaudient.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.06,1:56:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.06,1:56:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,where you hold something
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.06,1:56:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know everything about who the person is
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.06,1:56:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll forget the term for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.35,1:56:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychometry.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.35,1:56:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Which came on spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.35,1:56:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and somebody left
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.35,1:56:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a scarf in my office
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.35,1:56:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and I picked up the scarf
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.35,1:56:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and instantly it was like a loud knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.35,1:56:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of whose it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.35,1:56:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, this is Estelle's.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.35,1:56:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, look what I found.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.35,1:56:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, give me my scarf.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.35,1:56:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So it came on spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.35,1:56:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a long period of time
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.35,1:56:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,where you have your clairaudient,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.35,1:56:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,clairvoyant.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.39,1:56:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have distant vision.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.39,1:56:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drive
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.57,1:56:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state you've never been before
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.57,1:56:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without a map
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.57,1:56:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and instantly know how to get past
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.57,1:56:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,all those lakes and all those complicated highways.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.57,1:56:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is picture where you're going
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.57,1:56:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you automatically go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.57,1:56:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's all kinds of different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.13,1:56:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is not to get glamorized by them
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.13,1:56:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,or caught by them
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.13,1:57:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and not to get fixated in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.13,1:57:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And not to have the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.13,1:57:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,think who it is because of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.13,1:57:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not you that's doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.13,1:57:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the aura,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.13,1:57:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,this energy, the auric field
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.13,1:57:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.13,1:57:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the witness of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.13,1:57:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you witness the very miraculous things
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.13,1:57:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,happening all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.13,1:57:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And also it had the power to heal things.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.13,1:57:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,People would sit down next to you
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.13,1:57:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and barely able
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.13,1:57:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to stand it
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.13,1:57:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and after five minutes they'd get up
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.13,1:57:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and walk away perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.18,1:57:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Left their cane there, everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.18,1:57:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that energy field is transformative.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.18,1:57:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's temporary,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.60,1:57:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,at least in myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.60,1:57:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very strong for at least five years.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.60,1:57:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It could also affect
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.50,1:57:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,electrical circuits
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.50,1:57:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and electrical phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.50,1:57:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Electronic equipment, essentially.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.50,1:57:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You could turn strobe lights on and off
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.50,1:57:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,on various things.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.50,1:57:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Amplifiers, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.50,1:58:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred watt amplifier,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.50,1:58:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a Macintosh amplifier went out.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.50,1:58:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy came to fix it
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.50,1:58:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and as he walks toward it
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.50,1:58:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the amplifier is perfect,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.50,1:58:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.50,1:58:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In my mind I'm thinking,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.50,1:58:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's perfect, there's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.50,1:58:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly the hundred watt amplifier went on.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.50,1:58:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy says, holy smokes.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.78,1:58:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, how did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.78,1:58:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I started talking to him about
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.78,1:58:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.78,1:58:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I don't know, I was doing the Course in Miracles and all of a sudden this kind of stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.78,1:58:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had exactly one copy left.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.78,1:58:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had bought 50 of them
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.78,1:58:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and given them away to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.78,1:58:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had exactly one copy left.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.78,1:58:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So this guy came to fix the amplifier,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.78,1:58:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessed what he thought was the miraculous,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.78,1:58:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,says I want the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.78,1:58:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,got the one book, walked out, said thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.78,1:58:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's obviously the karmic reason
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.78,1:58:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,why he came that day.
